my money locked in?","spans":[]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"\nNo. You can have access to your money in a few days, at any time, with a stocks and shares ISA or general investment account. Pension, Lifetime ISA and Junior ISA have withdrawal restrictions and conditions that may apply.","spans":[{"start":169,"end":222,"type":"hyperlink","data":{"link_type":"Web","url":"https://www.nutmeg.com/faq#how-easy-is-it-to-withdraw-money","target":"_blank"}}]}],"faqSection":[{"heading":[{"type":"heading2","text":"Who's it for?","spans":[]}],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"\n“I want my portfolio to be proactively managed by experts and invested in line with my values.”","spans":[]}]},{"heading":[{"type":"heading2","text":"What does the portfolio contain?","spans":[]}],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"\nOur socially responsible portfolios lean towards companies and bond issuers that have high environmental, social and governance (ESG) standards. We invest in exchange traded funds (or ETFs) that avoid companies engaged in controversial activities, while focusing on those that lead their peers on ESG.","spans":[{"start":185,"end":188,"type":"hyperlink","data":{"link_type":"Web","url":"https://www.nutmeg.com/how-we-invest/etf-guide"}}]}]},{"heading":[{"type":"heading2","text":"Is there ongoing management?","spans":[]}],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"\nYes. Like our fully managed style, our team of investment experts will monitor your portfolio for you. This means rebalancing when necessary, to ensure your portfolio is aligned at all times to your long-term objectives, and making strategic adjustments to the mix of investments.","spans":[{"start":15,"end":34,"type":"strong"},{"start":15,"end":34,"type":"hyperlink","data":{"link_type":"Web","url":"https://www.nutmeg.com/fully-managed-portfolios"}}]}]}]},{"type":"spacing_section","size":"xl","color":"white"},{"type":"rich_text","text":[{"type":"heading1","text":"This is the future of investing","spans":[{"start":0,"end":31,"type":"label","data":{"label":"label"}}]}],"spacing":"sm","alignment":"center","backrgoundColor":"white","noStack":true,"id":null},{"type":"rich_text","text":[{"type":"heading2","text":"Responsibility matters","spans":[{"start":0,"end":22,"type":"label","data":{"label":"label"}}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Radically transparent, focused on the long term, and focused on companies with good environmental, social and governance credentials, socially responsible investing (SRI) meets our criteria for what the future of investing should look like.","spans":[]},{"type":"heading2","text":"What's in the name?","spans":[{"start":0,"end":19,"type":"label","data":{"label":"label"}}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"We recognise the importance of ESG factors in delivering sustainable long-term returns and work alongside MSCI, a global leader in social responsibility research, to do so. We believe that to ignore the risks and opportunities arising from ESG would be a failure of our fiduciary responsibilities. And by engaging with these important issues, we build and manage portfolios that are better aligned with the broader objectives of society.","spans":[]},{"type":"heading2","text":"The E, the S, and the G","spans":[{"start":0,"end":23,"type":"label","data":{"label":"label"}}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"We score all Nutmeg portfolios – not just SRI portfolios – against a range of Environmental, Social and Governance factors so you can see the impact your investments are having.","spans":[]}],"spacing":"sm","alignment":"left","backrgoundColor":"white","noStack":false,"id":null},{"type":"rich_text","text":[{"type":"image","url":"https://prismic-io.s3.amazonaws.com/nutmegnewbrand/2a4a415d-cb4d-4844-ac71-0d5634f65322_Arrows.png","alt":null,"copyright":null,"dimensions":{"width":100,"height":50}}],"spacing":"default","alignment":"center","backrgoundColor":"white","noStack":true,"id":null},{"type":"selection_box","heading":{"text":"What other investment styles are availa